Package: raven
Version: 2.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Essential: no
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), adduser
Recommends: nagios-plugins-basic, nmap
Suggests: nagios-plugins, monitoring-plugins
Maintainer: Raven Development Team <dev@raven.local>
Description: Modern network monitoring and alerting system
 Raven is a lightweight, modern network monitoring system built in Go.
 It provides real-time monitoring of network hosts and services with
 a clean web interface, Prometheus metrics, and flexible alerting.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time host and service monitoring
  - Modern responsive web interface
  - Prometheus metrics integration
  - WebSocket-based live updates
  - Plugin-based check system
  - Network discovery with nmap integration
  - BoltDB embedded database
  - Systemd service integration
 .
 This package includes the main raven daemon and raven-discover utility
 for automatic network discovery and configuration generation.
